quran[5{c,v,t}:
6,138,"kehte hain yeh janwar aur yeh khait mehfooz hain, a nahi sirf wohi log kha satke hain jinhein hum khilana chahain, halaank yeh pabandi un ki khud sakhta hai phir kuch janwar hain jin par sawari aur baar bardari haraam kar di gayi hai aur kuch janwar hain jin par Allah ka naam nahi letay, aur yeh sab kuch unhon ne Allah par aftara kya hai, anqareeb Allah inhen un aftara pardaaz yun ka badla day ga"
6,139,"aur kehte hain ke jo kuch un janwaron ke pait mein hai yeh hamaray mardon ke liye makhsoos hai aur hamari aurton par haraam, lekin agar woh murda ho to dono is ke khanay mein shareek ho satke hain yeh baatein jo unhon ne ghurr li hain un ka badla Allah inhen day kar rahay ga yaqeenan woh hakeem hai aur sab baton ki usay khabar hai"
6,140,yaqeenan khasaray mein par gay woh log jinhon ne apni aulaad ko jahalat o nadani ki bana par qatal kya aur Allah ke diye hue rizaq ko Allah par aftara pardazi kar ke haraamtehra liya yaqeenan woh bhatak gay aur hargiz woh raah raast panay walon mein se nah thay
6,141,"woh Allah hi hai jis ne terhan terhan ke baagh aur takistaanaur nakhlistan peda kiye, khatiyan agayin jin se qisam qisam ke makolaat haasil hotay hain, Zaitoon aur aanar ke darakht peda kiye jin ke phal soorat mein mushaba aur mazay mein mukhtalif hotay hain khao un ki pedawar jab ke yeh phalay-n, aur Allah ka haq ada karo jab is ki fasal katu, aur hadd se nah guzro ke Allah hadd se guzarnay walon ko pasand nahi karta"
6,142,phir wohi hai jis ne maweshion mein se woh janwar bhi peda kiye jin se sawari o baar bardari ka kaam liya jata hai aur woh bhi jo khanay aur bichenay ke kaam atay hain khao unn cheezon mein se jo Allah ne tumhe bakhsh hain aur shetan ki pairo y nah karo ke woh tumhara khula dushman hai
